<m1>SUNRISE<ql>
<m2><ql>
<m1><ep>
<m0>   <m0>HELPING OUT: <m0>Anyone who goes to see the new movie <m0>Twister <m0>this weekend at Sawgrass Mills mall in Sunrise can volunteer to help in case one hits South Florida.<ep>
   The American Red Cross and Cobb Movie Theater have teamed up to give everyone who buys a ticket information titled ``Are You Ready for a Tornado?''<ep>
   The Red Cross also will be on hand with other information and to recruit volunteers to help during a disaster. Hurricane season is less than a month away, officials said.<ql>
